spells.description:
Equip: Upon entering combat, and every 60 sec, gain either Massive or Miniature for 30 sec.

Miniature
Reduces your size by 20%, and increases your Speed by 1,236 and Haste by 8,277.

Massive
Increases your size by 20%, maximum health by 316,425, and Intellect by 7,970.

description: With an elixir as unpredictable as Noggenfogger's, you never know if to expect pirates or confusion.
